{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Idle Colony is a game about little creatures and big numbers that will make your dopamine go up and your worries go down. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Merge</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine two fruits of the same tier into the next one. 1$, 2$, 4$, 8$... This process generates an exponential amount of money as you make your way up to bigger fruits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843640/extras/gif_merge.gif?t=1734361262\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Upgrade</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock buildings to uncover always more options to leverage your income. As cash comes in, it goes out, to come back even faster! Improve every aspect of your economy to make the best out of it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843640/extras/gif_building.gif?t=1734361262\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Automate</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will start with a sapling that you'll have to manually water and harvest, but soon enough you'll be able to recruit thousands of na\u00efve creatures to assist you in your endeavor. They collect, fertilize, chop down, plant trees, create machines... and they love it!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843640/extras/gif_walking.gif?t=1734361262\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Prestige</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Now that you've got a wok full of delicious fruits and an army of colonists dedicated to you, it is time to perform the ritual... Sacrifice your colony to access powerful technologies and go even further next time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843640/extras/ritutu.png?t=1734361262\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Synergize</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through your progress, you'll earn two unique currencies to spend with care. Find the best strategies by carefully picking your technologies and special upgrades. Your choices will make the difference between millions and quintillions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2843640/extras/wokfilled.png?t=1734361262\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>A word of the author:</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I've been crafting games for a couple years, pursuing my childhood dream of making a living by creating fun things. I'm doing everything in my games: music, engine, art... and I love to talk with you all to improve my work through your feedback.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You're welcome anytime to have a chat on Discord (link on the right panel).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Baobabos","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2843640/dca349549a1608dcbf1e7ce7d79402253011dd5e.jpg"},{"name":"Big tree","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2843640/5a07f2740478c66dce08e5dc666fd32d2d23ad48.jpg"},{"name":"Unlimited","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2843640/4b126dc1dd2d81988c571bd7ba366c94da30cfff.jpg"},{"name":"Eternal light","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2843640/41bd84d16e8bf4d2838cc5bebd0343c9e5f50e3f.jpg"},{"name":"Rainbomelon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2843640/d52a47490ab98d9080b82ff0662799a838d307ec.jpg"},{"name":"CPU meltdown","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2843640/859366a2